<L>__{interior tent night}
<A>__{we hear the approach of a horse, and then the bodyguard enters the tent.}
<C>__{bodyguard}
<D>__{holiness, this has come for you.}
<A>__{the bodyguard hands the boy a parcel. tenzin gyatso unwraps it. his flashlight. it works. a pause, and then tenzin gyatso sits in front of the thangka of penden lhamo. he reads from the scripture pages laid out on the low table. he reads by flashlight.}
